Marija Abney, [[wikipedia:Janeshia Adams-Ginyard|Janeshia Adams-Ginyard]], Maria Hippolyte, Marie Mouroum, Jénel Stevens, Zola Williams, Christine Hollingsworth, and Shaunette Renée Wilson portray the other members of the Dora Milaje. [[wikipedia:Sope Aluko|Sope Aluko]] appears as [[Shaman (Earth-199999)|Shaman]]. [[Stan Lee]] makes an cameo as a gambler. [[wikipedia:Lucy Hockings|Lucy Hockings]] appears as herself. [[wikipedia:Bambadjan Bamba|Bambadjan Bamba]] portrays the militant leader. Alex Hibbert appears as an Oakland kid. [[wikipedia:Trevor Noah|Trevor Noah]] makes a cameo as Griot. [[wikipedia:Sebastian Stan|Sebastian Stan]] makes an uncredited appearance in the post-credits scene as [[James Barnes (Earth-199999)|Bucky Barnes]], now going by the alias "White Wolf". 

